t;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a HLV Gareth Southgate sau tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f2i n\u1ee3 tr\u1eadn thua B\u1ec9 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng khi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018, v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n k\u00e9m ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. T\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Thomas Meunier v\u00e0 Eden Hazard \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh-461-191191.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ec9 2-0 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/123.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Gareth Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black;\nmso-themecolor:text1\">Ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Tam S\u01b0 \u00fd th\u1ee9c r\u00f5 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 \u00f4ng \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e2u tr\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p c\u00f3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch h\u1ea1ng t\u01b0 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay. HLV Gareth Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn </span><span style=\"color:black\">B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 World Cup kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n v\u00ec nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u00fd th\u1ee9c r\u00f5 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 l\u1eeba d\u1ed1i b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\">\u201cC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i g\u00ec h\u01a1n \u1edf h\u1ecd qua 7 tu\u1ea7n s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean nhau v\u1eeba qua. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u1edf World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng hi\u1ec3u n\u00f3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean tr\u00ean c\u1ea3 mong \u0111\u1ee3i ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 ra sao. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn xa h\u01a1n n\u1eefa t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:black\">\u201c\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i CLB \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 do mua v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 tay \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, trong khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u00fd th\u1ee9c h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. Hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1edf World Cup n\u0103m nay s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u1ea5m g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eabu m\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-can-dich-thu-tu-world-cup-thanh-cong-nhat-tu-giay-vang-cua-kane-den-cach-mang-cua-southgate-421-191207.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/anh-can-dich-thu-tu-world-cup-thanh-cong-nhat-tu-giay-vang-cua-kane-den-cach-mang-cua-southgate.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-can-dich-thu-tu-world-cup-thanh-cong-nhat-tu-giay-vang-cua-kane-den-cach-mang-cua-southgate-421-191207.html\">Anh c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 World Cup: Th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u201cnh\u1ea1t\u201d, t\u1eeb gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Kane \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a Southgate</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f2i n\u1ee3 b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn thua th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u1eadm h\u01a1n \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Anh c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1261","checkdouble":"191214"},{"date":"04:51 15/07","title":"Jose Mourinho: \"\u0110T Anh sau World Cup 2018 \u0111ang c\u00f3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/jose-mourinho-noi-ve-dt-anh-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng theo nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho, \u0110T Anh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng.</h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh-461-191191.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/211837-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh-461-191191.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ec9 2-0 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nMeunier v\u00e0 Hazard gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh trong tr\u1eadn tranh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Ph\u1ea3i ra v\u1ec1 tr\u1eafng tay nh\u01b0ng Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa h\u01a1n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai khi b\u1ed9 khung HLV Gareth Southgate s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jose Mourinho n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jose Mourinho n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/jose-mourinho-noi-ve-dt-anh-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>D\u00f9 sao th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Gareth Southgate c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo HLV Jose Mourinho n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 nh\u1edd \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu l\u1edbn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c: &quot;R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u1ecd v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p gi\u1eefa Gareth Southgate c\u00f9ng tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Steve Holland, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;H\u1ecd duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 s\u1edf t\u1ed1t v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, Anh v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n kh\u00e1c khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Anh c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m th\u1ebf, ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i v\u00e0 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jose Mourinho nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh r\u1eb1ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb: &quot;Anh s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf cho s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-southgate-noi-ve-tran-thua-cua-dt-anh-465-191200.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/hlv-southgate-noi-ve-tran-thua-cua-dt-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-southgate-noi-ve-tran-thua-cua-dt-anh-465-191200.html\">HLV Southgate n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh: Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3o t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n</span><br>\r\nHLV Gareth Southgate b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o d\u00f9 \u0110T Anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 thua B\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&quot;Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o \u0110T Ph\u00e1p m\u00e0 xem, \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u0169ng di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7. \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ngo\u00e0i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u00edt s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chinh chi\u1ebfn \u1edf k\u1ef3 Euro v\u00e0 World Cup t\u1edbi&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, \u0110T Anh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i trung b\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i (26 tu\u1ed5i). Sau tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba, World Cup 2018 c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 chung k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 22h00 ng\u00e0y 15/7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-giup-bi-danh-bai-dt-anh-de-dang-466-191208.html\">3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-chien-thang-lich-su-cua-dt-bi-truoc-anh-469-191205.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-hazard-dich-than-tuyen-bo-muon-roi-chelsea-172-191203.html\">N\u00f3ng: Hazard \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nothing-is-coming-home-dau-la-ly-do-khien-dt-anh-trang-tay-tai-world-cup-2018-421-191202.html\">Nothing is coming home: \u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Anh tr\u1eafng tay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/croatia-co-nguy-co-mat-perisic-tai-tran-chung-ket-world-cup-421-191199.html\">Croatia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/harry-kane-len-tieng-sau-tran-thua-bi-465-191196.html\">Harry Kane n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i trong tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1260","checkdouble":"191215"},{"date":"05:56 15/07","title":"Harry Kane h\u1ea1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Euro 2020","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/harry-kane-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-euro-2020.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u l\u1ea1c quan h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Harry Kane sau tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Thua c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, tuy nhi\u00ean World Cup 2018 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ngo\u00e0i mong \u0111\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh khi c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 t\u01b0, \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Harry Kane l\u1ea1c quan v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Kane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Harry Kane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/harry-kane-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-euro-2020.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Kane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng 25 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cho Tam S\u01b0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Euro 2020 sau \u0111\u00e2y hai n\u0103m. Harry Kane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-bi-vs-anh-421-191185.html\" target=\"_blank\">B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018</span>: \u201cTh\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u sau \u0111\u00e2y hai n\u0103m.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cQuy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 v\u1eady b\u1edfi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ee3i ch\u1edd th\u00eam 20 n\u0103m n\u1eefa m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy tr\u00ec v\u00e0 d\u1ea7n d\u00e0 t\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn, ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Harry Kane c\u0169ng 99% s\u1ebd th\u1eafng danh hi\u1ec7u Gi\u00e0y V\u00e0ng World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn t\u00ednh thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a anh, v\u00f3i 5/6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft t\u1eeb hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu Tunisia v\u00e0 Panama, trong khi m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 s\u00fat penalty.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ng\u00f4i sao Tottenham n\u00f3i th\u00eam v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y: \u201cN\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 cho th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n knock-out, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. \u0110\u00e2y v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-la-vua-pha-luoi-nhat-nheo-nhat-421-191204.html\">Harry Kane l\u00e0 Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi... nh\u1ea1t nh\u1ebdo nh\u1ea5t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/harry-kane-len-tieng-sau-tran-thua-bi-465-191196.html\">Harry Kane n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i trong tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/kane-choi-that-vong-southgate-van-ra-suc-bao-ve-469-191217.html\">Harry Kane ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, Southgate v\u1eabn ra s\u1ee9c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/neville-chi-ra-nguyen-nhan-khien-kane-choi-te-truoc-bi-469-191218.html\">Neville ch\u1ec9 ra nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Harry Kane ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1259","checkdouble":"191216"},{"date":"05:02 15/07","title":"Kane ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, Southgate v\u1eabn ra s\u1ee9c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/kane-choi-that-vong-southgate-van-ra-suc-bao-ve.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Southgate l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Harry Kane \u1edf World Cup 2018 sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec3n Anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i St. Petersburg.</h2><h2>Kane g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kane nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018. Kane ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ebfn \u1edf 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 anh ra s\u00e2n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Kane \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi n\u1ed5i d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. Anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u00fat tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. </div>\r\n<h2>HLV Southgate b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Kane\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Southgate b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Kane sau tr\u1eadn thua B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Southgate b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Kane sau tr\u1eadn thua B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/kane-choi-that-vong-southgate-van-ra-suc-bao-ve.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV\u00a0Southgate b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Kane sau tr\u1eadn thua\u00a0B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 s\u1ef1 sa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Kane so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u01b0ng HLV Southgate v\u1eabn ra s\u1ee9c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng sau tr\u1eadn thua B\u1ec9.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<em>\u201cTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m nay l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 7 sau m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec1m ch\u1ebf c\u1ea3m x\u00fac tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d, Southgate \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i khi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a Kane.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cS\u1ebd th\u1eadt sai l\u1ea7m khi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m nay. B\u1edfi v\u00ec th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n sung m\u00e3n. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Kane \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 huy \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng lan t\u1ecfa truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng t\u1eebng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi \u0111\u00edch \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng n\u00ean t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh. B\u1edfi v\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o r\u1ea5t s\u00e2u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n khi tham d\u1ef1 World Cup ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh\u201d.</em><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh:</strong><br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh-461-191191.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ec9 2-0 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nothing-is-coming-home-dau-la-ly-do-khien-dt-anh-trang-tay-tai-world-cup-2018-421-191202.html\">Nothing is coming home: \u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Anh tr\u1eafng tay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1258","checkdouble":"191217"},{"date":"05:55 15/07","title":"Neville ch\u1ec9 ra nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Kane ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/neville-chi-ra-nguyen-nhan-khien-kane-choi-te-truoc-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gary Neville cho r\u1eb1ng Harry Kane kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u00ec th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea1n ki\u1ec7t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</h2><h2>Kane ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Harry Kane \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean khi Anh \u0111\u1ec3 thua B\u1ec9 0-2 trong tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba v\u1eeba qua. Kane th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u00fat tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch t\u1ea1i St. Petersburg. Nh\u01b0ng anh v\u1eabn \u0111ang n\u1eafm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKane \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u World Cup v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Anh l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ghi hat-trick \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng g\u1eb7p Panama. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Tottenham ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Colombia \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, Kane kh\u00f4ng ghi th\u00eam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o. Anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00fa s\u00fat tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch n\u00e0o trong 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf World Cup.</div>\r\n<h2>Neville ch\u1ec9 ra nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neville ch\u1ec9 ra nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Kane g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Neville ch\u1ec9 ra nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Kane g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/neville-chi-ra-nguyen-nhan-khien-kane-choi-te-truoc-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kane g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Gary Neville, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi\u1ebfu thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Kane n\u1eb1m \u1edf y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean k\u00eanh ITV sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9, Neville chia s\u1ebb:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cKane s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng k\u1ebb t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Colombia, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1edfi v\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh t\u1edbi 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTheo t\u00f4i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n cho l\u1eafm. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf hi\u1ec7p hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi B\u1ec9, khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9, Kane v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n nh\u01b0ng Kane kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh cho nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh. V\u1edbi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, Kane ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c sau tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh-461-191191.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ec9 2-0 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/harry-kane-len-tieng-sau-tran-thua-bi-465-191196.html\">Harry Kane n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i trong tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1257","checkdouble":"191218"},{"date":"06:35 15/07","title":"L\u1ecbch 