layercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Karim Benzema c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, HLV Carlo Ancelotti \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n San Paolo.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Benzema</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Carlo Ancelotti \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay th\u1ebf Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Napoli t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Paolo m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Karim Benzema c\u1ee7a Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Karim Benzema c\u1ee7a Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/27/Napoli-muon-mua-Karim-Benzema-cua-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Benzema</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAncelotti \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Karim Benzema c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, HLV Carlo Ancelotti \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n San Paolo.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Benzema lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ghi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng anh l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Ancelotti \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Benzema v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n Napoli chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987. Theo La Sexta, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-real-xac-nhan-ronaldo-cap-ben-juventus-180-190888.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span>, n\u1ebfu Benzema c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Napoli, hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nhau \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Napoli c\u00f3 Benzema</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef Ronaldo \u1edf l\u1ea1i, vi\u1ec7c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Benzema mo ty so sau sai sot cua Karius\" title=\"Benzema m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 sau sai s\u00f3t c\u1ee7a Karius\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/27/ronaldo-va-benzema-sap-doi-dau-nhau-o-serie-a.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 nh\u1ea3 Benzema cho Napoli</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Ronaldo l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00eanh m\u00f4ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Los Blancos, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u01b0u ti\u00ean gi\u1eef Benzema, Isco, Bale hay Asensio. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Napoli ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao 31 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y t\u00e2n HLV Lopetegui c\u1ee7a Real kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Benzema v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1255","checkdouble":"191165"}]}